sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Nginx
    participant Gateway
    participant ServiceCatalog
    participant CatalogDB

    Note over Admin,CatalogDB: Admin has already logged in.
    Note over Admin: Admin has already been on newbook.html<br/>REF:UC-07 Loading newbook page

    Admin           ->>  Nginx          :   HTTP POST http://libofalex.com/addbook <br/>AddBookRequest
    Nginx           ->>  Gateway        :   HTTP POST http://server-gateway/addbook <br/>AddBookRequest
    Gateway         ->>  Gateway        :   User has Admin Role
    alt Unsuccessfull
        Gateway     -->> Nginx          :   HTTP 401 Unauthorized
        Nginx       -->> Admin          :   HTTP 401 Unauthorized
    else Successfull
        Gateway     ->>  ServiceCatalog :   HTTP POST http://service-catalog.com/api/v1/books <br/>AddBookRequest
        ServiceCatalog ->> CatalogDB    :   save BookEntity
        CatalogDB   -->> ServiceCatalog :   ok
        ServiceCatalog -->> Gateway     :   HTTP 200 OK AddBookResponse
        Gateway     -->>  Nginx         :   HTTP 200 OK AddBookResponse
        Nginx       -->>  Admin         :   HTTP 200 OK AddBookResponse
    end